Package org.alljoyn.bus

This package holds all of the AllJoyn code for creating and using interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AuthListener
    Authentication listeners are responsible for handling AllJoyn authentication requests.
    BusObject
    Implemented by classes that are AllJoyn bus objects.
    BusObjectListener
    Implemented by a user-defined BusObject that is interested in handling registration and unregistration notifications.
    IntrospectionListener
    Implemented by a user-defined BusObject that is interested in customizing the D-Bus introspection XML presented to remote nodes.
    IntrospectionWithDescriptionListener
    Implemented by a user-defined BusObject that is interested in customizing the AllJoyn introspection XML presented to remote nodes.
    KeyStoreListener
    Implemented by a user-defined class that is responsible for loading and storing keys.
    SecurityViolationListener
    Allows an application to monitor security violations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthListener.AuthRequest
    Authentication request.
    AuthListener.CertificateRequest
    Authentication request for a chain of PEM-encoded X509 certificates.
    AuthListener.Credentials
    Authentication credentials set via authentication requests.
    AuthListener.ExpirationRequest
    Authentication request to set an expiration time for the credentials.
    AuthListener.LogonEntryRequest
    Authentication request for a logon entry.
    AuthListener.PasswordRequest
    Authentication request for a password, pincode, or passphrase.
    AuthListener.PrivateKeyRequest
    Authentication request for a PEM encoded private key.
    AuthListener.UserNameRequest
    Authentication request for a user name.
    AuthListener.VerifyRequest
    Authentication request for verification of a certificate chain from a remote peer.
    BusAttachment
    A connection to a message bus.
    BusListener
    Bus listeners are responsible for handling callbacks from the AllJoyn system.
    MessageContext
    Contains information about a specific method call or signal message.
    Mutable
    The underlying C++ implementation of the AllJoyn bus is fond of using in/out parameters.
    Mutable.IntegerValue
    A class providing inout parameter semantics for Java ints.
    Mutable.ShortValue
    A class providing inout parameter semantics for Java shorts.
    Mutable.StringValue
    A class providing [in,out] parameter semantics for Java Strings.
    OnJoinSessionListener
    An OnJoinSessionListener is responsible for receiving completion indications from asynchronous join operations.
    OnPingListener
    An OnPingListener is responsible for receiving completion indications from asynchronous ping operations.
    PasswordManager
    Class to allow the user or application to set credentials used for the authentication of thin clients.
    ProxyBusObject
    A bus object that exists and is managed by some other connection to the bus.
    SessionListener
    A SessionListener is responsible for handling session related callbacks from the AllJoyn system.
    SessionOpts  
    SessionPortListener
    A SessionPortListener is responsible for handling session port related callbacks from the AllJoyn system.
    SignalEmitter
    A helper proxy used by BusObjects to send signals.
    Translator  
    Variant
    A DBus/AllJoyn datatype whose type information is encoded into the value field.
    VariantTypeReference<T>
    Used when calling Variant.getObject(Class) where the wrapped object is a generic type such as Map<K, V>.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BusAttachment.RemoteMessage
    Policy for handling messages received from remote devices.
    SignalEmitter.GlobalBroadcast
    Controls behavior of broadcast signals (null desintation).
    Status
    Standard function return codes for this package.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AnnotationBusException
    AllJoyn annotation related exceptions.
    BusException
    Base class of AllJoyn exceptions.
    ErrorReplyBusException
    AllJoyn ERROR message exceptions.
    MarshalBusException
    AllJoyn marshalling related exceptions.

Package org.alljoyn.bus Description

This package holds all of the AllJoyn code for creating and using interfaces.
